cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "GlobalSat DG-388 .gpl Parser"
abstract: "First open-source decoder for the GlobalSat DG-388 GPS data logger's proprietary .gpl binary format. Converts .gpl track files to CSV or GPX with full coordinate, altitude, speed, heading, and timestamp recovery. Pure Python, no dependencies."
authors:
